arashtra%20Police%2C%20the%20local%20police%20had%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20launched%20an%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForensic%20and%20crime%20teams%20were%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20around%205%3A30%20pm%2C%20we%20received%20a%20call%20at%20the%20control%20room%20about%20a%20suspected%20hanging%20case.%20When%20the%20Hulimavu%20police%20reached%20the%20house%2C%20they%20found%20the%20door%20locked.%20After%20gaining%20entry%2C%20they%20found%20a%20suitcase%20in%20the%20bathroom%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sarah%20Fatima%2C%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20the%20local%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forensics%20team%20opened%20the%20suitcase%20and%20found%20the%20body%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20body%20of%20the%20woman%20is%20intact%20and%20not%20in%20pieces%20(as%20is%20usually%20the%20case%20with%20suitcase%20murders)%20--%20but%20there%20are%20severe%20injury%20marks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20know%20the%20extent%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20injuries%20once%20we%20receive%20the%20postmortem%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20she%20added%2C%20initially%20drew%20a%20blank%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20trace%20her%20husband.%20Later%2C%20they%20were%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20detained.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20now%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHUSBAND%20ARRESTED%20FROM%20PUNE%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20Sambekar%20had%20fled%20to%20Pune%20following%20the%20murder%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20However%2C%20swift%20coordination%20between%20Hulimavu%20and%20Pune%20police%20-%20enabled%20after%20tracking%20his%20call%20records%20-%20led%20to%20the%20man's%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20from%20Bengaluru%20has%20now%20left%20for%20Pune%20to%20bring%20the%20suspect%20back%20for%20further%20interrogation%20and%20legal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20is%20on%20into%20the%20motive%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20investigating%20further%20to%20understand%20what%20exactly%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%2C%20she%20said%2C%20got%20married%20two%20years%20ago.%20They%20are%20from%20Maharashtra%20and%20had%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20two%20months%20ago%20for%20work.%20He%20works%20as%20a%20project%20manager%20at%20an%20IT%20company.%20She%20was%20a%20housewife%20and%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743102120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F62bet9dg_bengaluru-suitcase-murder_625x300_28_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomans-body-found-stuffed-in-suitcase-in-bengaluru-flat-husband-arrested-from-pune-8027330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman's%20body%20has%20been%20found%20stuffed%20in%20a%20suitcase%20at%20a%20residence%20near%20Hulimavu%2C%20sending%20shockwaves%20across%20Bengaluru.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomans-body-found-stuffed-in-suitcase-in-bengaluru-flat-husband-arrested-from-pune-8027330%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Could%20Supply%20Small%20Nuclear%20Power%20Plant%20For%20Musk's%20Mars%20Mission%3A%20Russian%20Envoy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussia%20could%20supply%20a%20small%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20for%20a%20mission%20to%20Mars%20planned%20by%20billionaire%20entrepreneur%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20international%20cooperation%20envoy%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20envoy%2C%20Kirill%20Dmitriev%2C%20said%20Moscow%20could%20discuss%20the%20offer%20with%20Musk%20by%20video%20conference.%20It%20was%20the%20second%20time%20Dmitriev%20has%20spoken%20of%20potential%20cooperation%20with%20Musk%20this%20month.