20US%20Tariffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20spell%20out%20India's%20response%20to%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20threat%20of%20tariff%20war%2C%20alleging%20that%20no%20discussion%20in%20parliament%20or%20consultation%20with%20Opposition%20parties%20has%20been%20held%20over%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20for%20finding%20common%20ground%20with%20other%20nations%20that%20share%20the%20same%20interests%20in%20pushing%20back%20against%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20and%20warned%20that%20if%20Mr%20Trump%20starts%20picking%20out%20individual%20countries%20and%20applying%20different%20tariffs%2C%20the%20affected%20nations%20could%20be%20left%20to%20fend%20on%20their%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%20if%20the%20Indian%20government's%20perception%20is%20that%20America%20is%20taking%20one%20step%20forward%20and%20two%20steps%20backwards%2C%20it%20must%20have%20a%20policy%20to%20counteract%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20it%20can't%20be%20in%20uncertainty.%20Of%20course%2C%20Americans%20are%20uncertain%2C%20let's%20assume%20so.%20But%20you%20must%20have%20alternative%20scenarios.%20What%20if%20they%20take%20one%20step%20forward%3F%20What%20is%20our%20response%3F%20What%20if%20they%20take%20two%20steps%20backward%3F%20What%20is%20our%20response%3F%20And%20that%20response%20need%20not%20be%20made%20public%20to%20the%20whole%20world%2C%20but%20at%20least%20there%20must%20be%20a%20statement%20in%20parliament%2C%20or%20there%20must%20be%20a%20consultation%20with%20opposition%20parties.%20We%20are%20completely%20in%20the%20dark%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20who%20was%20Union%20finance%20minister%20under%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20my%20information%20is%2C%20most%20ministers%20are%20in%20the%20dark.%20Who%20is%20involved%20in%20making%20this%20reactive%20policy%20to%20America's%20uncertain%20policy%3F%20I%20don't%20know.%20Nobody%20seems%20to%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20slap%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20all%20auto%20imports%20has%20cast%20uncertainty%20over%20India's%20nearly%20%247%20billion%20of%20exports%20to%20the%20US%2C%20which%20industry%20fears%20could%20squeeze%20margins.%20Automobiles%20and%20car%20parts%20imported%20to%20the%20US%20would%20face%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20starting%20April%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20is%20not%20a%20big%20exporter%20of%20cars%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Tata%20Motors'%20luxury%20car%20subsidiary%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover%20(JLR)%20is%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20the%20American%20market.%20Indian%20auto%20ancillary%20firms%20will%20see%20the%20biggest%20hit%20as%20they%20export%20a%20lot%20of%20components%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20revenue%20of%20India's%20auto%20component%20sector%20is%20derived%20from%20exports.%20Of%20this%2C%2027%20per%20cent%20is%20to%20the%20US%20market%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F8bi7niog_shipping-generic_625x300_12_February_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20government%20is%20making%20sort%20of%20impromptu%2C%20unilateral%2C%20knee-jerk%20decisions.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20Budget%20speech%2C%20they%20got%20rid%20of%20the%202%20per%20cent%20tax.%20Day%20before%20yesterday%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20announced%20that%20the%206%20per%20cent%20digital%20service%20tax%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20the%20Google%20tax%2C%20will%20go.%20Now%2C%20what%20more%20are%20they%20going%20to%20concede%20to%20Mr%20Trump%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20wish%20to%20have%20a%20public%20discussion%20in%20parliament%2C%20then%20you%20should%20at%20least%20invite%20the%20principal%20opposition%20parties%20which%20are%20represented%20in%20parliament%20and%20take%20leaders%20into%20confidence%20of%20what%20alternative%20scenarios%20are%20being%20worked%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram%20defended%20his%20comment%20that%20most%20ministers%20are%20in%20the%20dark%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20only%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20and%20perhaps%20the%20commerce%20minister%20who%20went%20on%20a%20delegation%20to%20the%20US%20are%20privy%20to%20what%20is%20going%20on.%20I%20don't%20think%20other%20ministers%20know.%20I'm%20sure%20the%20agriculture%20minister%20does%20not%20know.%20I'm%20sure%20the%20industries%20minister%20does%20not%20know.%20But%20they%20are%20making%20concessions%3F%20I%20don't%20know.%20Are%20you%20making%20concessions%20on%20agriculture%3F%20Are%20you%20making%20concessions%20on%20industrial%20goods%3F%20Are%20you%20making%20concessions%20on%20intellectual%20property%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20anybody%20knows%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Union%20finance%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20should%20put%20its%20interest%20first%2C%20but%20many%20countries%20are%20finding%20common%20ground%20in%20acknowledging%20that%20unilateral%20tariffs%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%20are%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjh0f2qmo_us-president-donald-trump_625x300_27_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20WTO%20rules%3B%20there%20are%20multilateral%20and%20bilateral%20trade%20agreements%3B%20there%20are%20international%20laws%20and%20conventions.%20So%20if%20you%20want%20to%20rewrite%20the%20tariffs%20of%20several%20countries%2C%20you%20must%20hold%20a%20discussion.%20This%20is%20what%20Prime%20Minister%20Mark%20Carney%20of%20Canada%20is%20doing.%20He%20has%20taken%20his%20parliament%20into%20confidence%2C%20at%20least%20the%20leaders%20into%20confidence.%20And%20he%20says%20we%20will%20coordinate%20with%20the%20European%20countries%20and%20respond%20to%20Mr%20Trump's%20unilateral%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I'm%20sure%20the%20oil%20producing%20countries%20are%20also%20coordinating%20among%20themselves.%20We%20are%20a%20major%20agricultural%20exporter.%20We%20are%20a%20major%20textile%20exporter.%20We%20also%20export%20a%20lot%20of%20industrial%20goods.%20So%20we%20must%20band%20together%20with%20countries%20which%20are%20in%20the%20world%20market%20for%20agricultural%20exports%2C%20textile%20exports%2C%20and%20industrial%20goods%20exports%2C%20and%20evolve%20a%20common%20approach.%20You%20see%2C%20if%20he%20%5BMr%20Trump%5D%20picks%20one%20country%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20imposes%20tariffs%2C%20it%20will%20ruin%20the%20economy%20of%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuppose%20he%20picks%20India%2C%20and%20he%20leaves%20other%20countries%20out.%20Suppose%20President%20Trump%20picks%20India%20and%20says%2C%20'these%20are%20the%20tariffs%20from%20goods%20exported%20from%20India'%2C%20we'll%20be%20ruined.%20In%20a%20matter%20of%20three%20to%20six%20months%2C%20our%20economy%20will%20be%20ruined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20afraid%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20not%20going%20to%20group%20all%20the%20countries%20together%20and%20impose%20universal%20tariffs.%20He's%20giving%20a%20number%20for%20each%20country%2C%20what%20they%20have%20calculated%2C%20I'm%20told%2C%20calculated%20as%20the%20average%20weighted%20trade%20tariff.%20And%20he's%2