E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20ban%20on%20offering%20%3Cem%3E'namaz'%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20roads%20or%20rooftops%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Sambhal%20district%2C%20Mr%20Vadra%20said%20people%20turn%20to%20their%20faith%20in%20times%20of%20difficulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20a%20person%20is%20in%20trouble%2C%20he%20remembers%20his%20God%2C%20not%20a%20minister%2C%20because%20no%20minister%20is%20going%20to%20come%20at%20that%20time.%20Those%20who%20go%20to%20the%20temple%20or%20mosque%20remember%20the%20difficult%20times%20and%20pray%20so%20that%20their%20troubles%20are%20averted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20BJP%20indulges%20in%20politics%20of%20religion%20or%20divides%20on%20religious%20lines%20by%20saying%20that%20%3Cem%3E'namaz'%3C%2Fem%3E%20cannot%20be%20offered%20and%20meat%20shops%20should%20be%20closed%20or%20the%20names%20of%20places%20named%20after%20Aurangzeb%20should%20be%20changed%2C%20then%20this%20kind%20of%20politics%20is%20harmful.%20This%20will%20not%20bring%20progress%2C%20and%20everyone%20will%20be%20divided%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vadra%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20says%20%3Cem%3E'batoge%20to%20katoge'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(if%20you%20are%20divided%2C%20you%20will%20suffer)...%20if%20any%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20such%20thinking%2C%20then%20we%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20move%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743091320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fnh9fpui8_robert-vadra_625x300_27_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-skipped-kumbh-to-avoid-incovenience-to-pilgrims-robert-vadra-8026193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rober