%20marry%20her%20lover.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBablu%20got%20Radhika%20married%20as%20per%20Hindu%20customs%20at%20a%20Shiva%20temple%20and%20also%20completed%20the%20legal%20process%20by%20becoming%20a%20witness%20and%20getting%20the%20marriage%20notified%20in%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20labourer%20also%20decided%20to%20take%20custody%20of%20his%20two%20children%20with%20Radhika%20and%20said%20he%20would%20raise%20them%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20showed%20Radhika%20marrying%20Vikas%20surrounded%20by%20her%20children%20and%20other%20villagers.%20Vikas%20can%20be%20seen%20applying%20sindoor%20to%20Radhika's%20forehead%20after%20they%20exchange%20garlands%20and%20Bablu%20even%20poses%20for%20a%20photo%20with%20the%20couple%20after%20their%20marriage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Wanted%20To%20Avoid%20Harm'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20he%20had%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20unusual%20step%2C%20Bablu%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20decided%20to%20arrange%20their%20marriage%20to%20avoid%20potential%20harm%20to%20myself.%20In%20recent%20days%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20husbands%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20their%20wives...%20After%20seeing%20what%20happened%20in%20Meerut%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20get%20my%20wife%20married%20to%20her%20lover%20so%20that%20we%20can%20both%20live%20peacefully.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20marriage%20since%20he%20and%20Radhika%20are%20not%20divorced%2C%20Bablu%20said%20it%20was%20legal%20because%20it%20took%20place%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20villagers%20and%20no%20family%20members%20objected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrigger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskan%20and%20her%20lover%20Sahil%20drugged%20and%20killed%20her%20husband%20Saurabh%2C%20a%20former%20Navy%20officer%2C%20in%20Meerut%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20cut%20his%20body%20before%20dumping%20it%20in%20a%20drum%20lined%20with%20ceme