ms%20of%20working%20at%20a%20tech%20giant%20like%20Google%20or%20Facebook.%20Instead%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20running%20a%20tea%20stall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20studied%20computer%20science%2C%20hoping%20to%20get%20a%20good%20IT%20job.%20But%20there%20is%20tough%20competition%20in%20the%20field%2C%20and%20after%20the%20lockdown%2C%20many%20people%20lost%20their%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Aryan%20Srivastava%2C%20who%20has%20a%20BSc%20degree%20in%20Agriculture%2C%20had%20hoped%20to%20contribute%20to%20India's%20agricultural%20sector.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20found%20himself%20stuck%20in%20the%20job-seeking%20cycle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20no%20placements%20in%20my%20college.%20I%20thought%20my%20background%20in%20agriculture%20would%20provide%20me%20with%20opportunities%2C%20but%20there%20are%20fewer%20government%20vacancies.%20Even%20when%20there%20are%20openings%2C%20paper%20leaks%20ruin%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20students%20and%20job%20seekers%20have%20been%20left%20frustrated%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20opportunities%20and%20frequent%20delays%20in%20recruitment.%20Shailendra%20Mishra%20has%20already%20spent%20Rs%2030%2C000%20on%20application%20fees%2C%20books%2C%20and%20other%20expenses%20while%20preparing%20for%20government%20exams.%20Sonali%20Patel%20has%20been%20waiting%20for%20police%20recruitment%20results%20since%202019%2C%20but%20the%20outcome%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20maintains%20that%20the%20job%20situation%20is%20not%20as%20dire%20as%20it%20seems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20records%2C%20in%20July%202023%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%2025.82%20lakh%20unemployed%20individuals.%20By%20December%2C%20the%20number%20had%20gone%20up%20to%2026.17%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20instead%20of%20acknowledging%20an%20increase%2C%20the%20government%20has%20rebranded%20these%20individuals%20as%20%26quot%3BAspirational%20Youth%26quot%3B%2C%20whose%20number%20extend%20to%2029.36%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202020%20and%202024%2C%202%2C709%20job%20fairs%20were%20organised%2C%20resulting%20in%203.22%20lakh%20offer%20letters%20being%20issued.%20The%20government%2C%20though%2C%20has%20not%20disclosed%20how%20many%20candidates%20actually%20joined%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Skill%20Development%20Minister%20Gautam%20Tetwal%20defended%20the%20new%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20unemployed%20people%20registered%20in%20employment%20offices%20is%20different%20from%20the%20actual%20count.%20If%20a%20son%20works%20at%20his%20father's%20shop%20and%20is%20registered%20in%20an%20employment%20office%2C%20he%20is%20not%20unemployed.%20A%20person%20earning%20less%20than%20Rs%2012%2C646%20per%20month%20without%20steady%20work%20can%20be%20considered%20unemployed%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20the%20situation%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLA%20Pratap%20Grewal%20criticised%20the%20government's%20approach%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20renaming%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20manipulate%20statistics.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20government%20previously%20reported%2033%20lakh%20unemployed%20people%20in%20July.%20Now%2C%20it%20avoids%20sharing%20actual%20figures%2C%20fearing%20backlash.%20Instead%20of%20solving%20the%20crisis%2C%20they%20are%20simply%20renaming%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743086940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fg5et1fg_unemployment_625x300_01_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funemployed-no-they-are-aspirational-youth-says-madhya-pradesh-8025609%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government's%20approach%20to%20renaming%20has%20now%20extended%20beyond%20roads%20and%20districts%20to%20unemployment.%20The%20state%20has%20decided%20that%20unemployed%20youth%20will%20now%20be%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BAspirational%20Youth%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funemployed-no-they-are-aspirational-youth-says-madhya-pradesh-8025609%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NCLT%20orders%20status%20quo%20on%20shareholding%20of%20Aakash%20Educational%20Services%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743086672000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fnclt-orders-status-quo-on-shareholding-of-aakash-educational-services-125032701086_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20was%20on%20a%20plea%20by%20the%20resolution%20professional%20of%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Byju's%2C%20Think%20and%20Learn%20Pvt%20Ltd.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fnclt-orders-status-quo-on-shareholding-of-aakash-educational-services-125032701086_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Columbia%20University%20Betrayed%20Me%3A%20Indian%20Student%20Who%20Self-Deported%20To%20Canada%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERanjini%20Srinivasan%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20Indian%20PhD%20student%20in%20the%20US%20who%20self-deported%20to%20Canada%20after%20her%20student%20visa%20was%20revoked%20for%20allegedly%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bterror%20sympathizer%26quot%3B%2C%20opened%20up%20about%20her%20ordeal%20today.%20She%20even%20said%20that%20she%20feels%20'betrayed'%20by%20her%20alma%20mater%20-%20the%20renowned%20Columbia%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Srinivasan%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20supporter%20and%20sympathizer%20of%20Hamas%20-%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20organisation%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20region%20of%20Gaza.%20She%20was%20pursuing%20her%20doctorate%20in%20public%20planning%2C%20and%20was%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20completing%20her%20PhD%2C%20when%20the%20Trump%20administration%20revoked%20her%20student%20visa%20for%20her%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20propagating%20and%20aligning%20with%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20student%20visa%20was%20renewed%20in%20December%20-%20just%20a%20month%20before%20Trump's%20inauguration%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20She%20is%20now%20pinning%20her%20hope%20on%20Columbia%20University%20to%20consider%20her%20appeal%20and%20reinstate%20her%20enrollment.%20But%20she%20feels%20equally%20betrayed%20by%20Columbia%20for%20the%20treatment%20met%20to%20her%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%20five%20years%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20working%2C%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20maybe%20100%20hours%20a%20week%20sometimes.%20I%20never%20expected%20the%20institution%20to%20let%20me%20down.%20But%20it%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Al%20Jazeera%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Srinivasan%20was%20a%20Fulbright%20recipient%20at%20Columbia%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20Columbia%20comes%20to%20its%20senses%20and%20re-enrolls%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20hoping%20for%20fairness%20and%20justice%20from%20an%20institution%20of%20global%20repute.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20she%20has%20made%20all%20her%20academic%20submission%20and%20completed%20all%20the%20university's%20requirements%20needed%20to%20complete%20her%20PhD%20-%20hinting%20that%20it%20is%20now%20just%20a%20formality%20for%20the%20institution%20to%20award%20her%20her%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20requirements%20for%20my%20PhD%20are%20complete%2C%20and%20whatever%20is%20left%2C%20I%20don't%20even%20need%20to%20be%20in%20the%20US%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I'm%20trying%20to%20appeal%20to%20Columbia%26quot%3B%20for%20them%20to%20do%20their%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20ORDEAL%20AND%20THE%20ESCAPE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20her%20ordeal%2C%20Ms%20Srinivasan%20recalled%20how%20she%20got%20an%20email%20from%20the%20US%20Consulate%20in%20Chennai%20on%20March%205%20which%20stated%20that%20her%20student%20visa%20had%20been%20revoked%20indefinitely.%20Within%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20while%20she%20was%20still%20trying%20to%20understand%20what%20had%20happened%20by%20contacting%20officials%20at%20Columbia%20and%20her%20PhD%20group%2C%20agents%20from%20the%20United%20States'%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20showed%20up%20at%20her%20doorstep%2C%20possibly%20to%20detain%20her%20in%20order%20to%20deport%20her%20from%20the%20country.%20She%20didn't%20answer%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20evening%2C%20while%20she%20was%20not%20at%20home%2C%20the%20agents%20returned%2C%20asking%20for%20her.%20Her%20roommate%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20them.%20Hours%20later%2C%20another%20Columbia%20student%20Mahmoud%20Khalil%20was%20detained%20on%20campus%2C%20which%20led%20to%20unrest%20between%20students%20and%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Srinivasan%2C%20now%20fearing%20arrest%2C%20managed%20to%20escape%20with%20a%20bag%20containing%20her%20documents%2C%20essentials%2C%20and%20a%20few%20items%20of%20value.%20Agents%20were%20on%20a%20constant%20lookout%20for%20her%20while%20she%20was%20on%20the%20run.%20On%20March%2011%2C%20after%20evading%20officials%2C%20she%20somehow%20managed%20to%20fly%20out%20of%20New%20York%20on%20a%20flight%20to%20Canada%2C%20where%20she%20touched%20base%20with%20her%20relatives%20and%20friends%20who%20came%20to%20her%20rescue.%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20New%20York's%20LaGuardia%20Airport%20showed%20her%20lugging%20a%20bag%20with%20her%20belongings.%20The%20footage%20was%20shared%20widely%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Srinivasan%20recalled%20how%20she%20feared%20being%20arrested%20in%20the%20US.%20Four%20days%20later%2C%20Kristi%20Noem%2C%20Secretary%20of%20US'%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20labelled%20Ms%20Srinivasan%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20sympathiser%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20still%20not%20been%20a%20word%20on%20the%20incident%20by%20Columbia%20University.%20Their%20stand%20on%20the%20issue%20is%20not%20known.%20Even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20this%20report%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20statement%20issued%20by%20Columbia%20University.%20Whether%20or%20not%20the%20institution%20will%20investigate%20the%20matter%20and%20deal%20with%20it%20fairly%20is%20not%20known.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20not%20clear%20whether%20she%20was%20targeted%20only%20for%20her%20political%20views%20on%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%2C%20or%20if%20she%20was%20actually%20involved%20in%20any%20way%20for%20the%20charges%20made%20against%20her.%20It%20is%20also%20not%20known%20if%2C%20as%20a%20student%20of%20Columbia%2C%20she%20had%20entered%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20institution%20which%20forbids%20her%20from%20even%20speaking%20about%20her%20political%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20US%20Government%20has%20labelled%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bterror%20sympathiser%26quot%3B%2C%20no%20evidence%20of%20her%20actively%20being%20involved%20has%20been%20shared%20publicly%2C%20nor%20the%20grounds%20for%20the%20charges%20been%20clarified.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI'm%20fearful%20that%20even%20the%20most%20low-level%20political%20speech%20or%20just%20doing%20what%20we%20all%20do%20-%20like%20shout%20into%20the%20abyss%20that%20is%20social%20media%20-%20can%20turn%20into%20this%20dystopian%20nightmare%2C%20where%20somebody%20is%20calling%20you%20a%20terrorist%20sympathizer%20and%20making%20you%2C%20literally%2C%20fear%20for%20your%20life%20and%20your%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Srinivasan%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Srinivasan%2C%20currently%20in%20Canada%2C%20now%20lives%20with%20uncertainty%20and%20hope.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743086580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F9iu1q7bc_ranjini-srinivasan-indian-phd-student-at-columbia-self-deported_625x300_27_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcolumbia-university-betrayed-me-indian-phd-student-ranjini-srinivasan-who-self-deported-to-canada-8025361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ranjini%20Srinivasan%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20Indian%20PhD%20student%20in%20the%20US%20who%20self-deported%20to%20Canada%20after%20her%20student%20visa%20was%20revoked%20for%20allegedly%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bterror%20sympathizer%26quot%3B%2C%20opened%20up%20about%20her%20ordeal%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcolumbia-university-betrayed-me-indian-phd-student-ranjini-srinivasan-who-self-deported-to-canada-8025361%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMade%204%20Demands%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Said...%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20Lawyers%20In%20Judge%20Cash%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESix%20high%20court%20bar%20associations%20met%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20Collegium%20on%20Thursday%20to%20protest%20the%20transfer%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjustice-yashwant-varma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustice%20Yashwant%20Varma%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Delhi%20to%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%2C%20and%20present%20a%20list%20of%20four%20demands%2C%20including%20the%20start%20of%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20against%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Tiwari%2C%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20association%2C%20said%20the%20Collegium%2C%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20gave%20them%20a%20patient%20hearing%2C%20a