n%20to%20neutralise%20an%20infiltrating%20group%20of%20about%20five%20terrorists%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20whether%20it%20was%20the%20same%20group%20that%20had%20been%20evading%20an%20earlier%20cordon%20in%20Sanyal%20forest%20of%20Kathua%20region%20or%20another%20batch%20of%20freshly%20infiltrated%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20encounter%20triggered%20intense%20firing%20and%20explosions%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gunfight%2C%20centred%20near%20Jakhole%20village%20in%20the%20Ghati%20Juthana%20area%20of%20Rajbagh%2C%20involved%20a%20group%20of%20approximately%20five%20terrorists%20and%20an%20initial%20exchange%20of%20gunfire%20resulted%20in%20injuries%20to%20Special%20Police%20Officer%20Bharat%20Chalotra%2C%20who%20sustained%20facial%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20treated%20at%20a%20Kathua%20hospital%20before%20being%20transferred%20to%20Government%20Medical%20College%20Hospital%20in%20Jammu%2C%20where%20his%20condition%20was%20stated%20to%20be%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20that%20two%20terrorists%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20onslaught%20led%20by%20the%20Special%20Operations%20Group%20(SOG)%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20and%20assisted%20by%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20BSF%20and%20CRPF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20tension%2C%20three%20security%20personnel%2C%20including%20a%20Sub-Divisional%20Police%20Officer%20(SDPO)%2C%20were%20reportedly%20trapped%20near%20the%20gunfight's%20location%2C%20adjacent%20to%20a%20rivulet%20concealed%20by%20dense%20foliage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20a%20clear%20picture%20would%20emerge%20only%20after%20the%20ongoing%20encounter%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20mentioned%20that%20a%20group%20of%20terrorists%20were%20intercepted%20by%20the%20SOG%20in%20the%20Hiranagar%20sector%20of%20Kathua%20district%20on%20Sunday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20massive%20search%20operation%2C%20the%20terrorists%20managed%20to%20escape%20the%20initial%20cordon%2C%20the%20officials%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20is%20assumed%20that%20the%20same%20could%20have%20been%20possibly%20spotted%20near%20Jakhole%2C%20approximately%2030%20kilometers%20from%20the%20initial%20encounter%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorists%20were%20moving%20through%20the%20forest%20area%20when%20a%20police%20party%20headed%20by%20a%20SDPO%20moved%20in%20after%20getting%20specific%20information%2C%20the%20officials%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20came%20under%20heavy%20firing%20resulting%20in%20the%20gunfight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReinforcements%20from%20the%20police%2C%20army%2C%20and%20CRPF%20were%20immediately%20deployed%20to%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quiet%20village%20Suffain%20in%20Kathua%20district%20was%20shattered%20by%20the%20relentless%20sounds%20of%20gunfire%2C%20grenades%2C%20and%20rocket%20fire%20as%20a%20fierce%20exchange%20raged%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20punctuated%20by%20a%20series%20of%20powerful%20explosions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20group%20of%20terrorists%20was%20intercepted%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20within%20a%20'dhok'%2C%20a%20local%20term%20for%20an%20enclosure%20in%20a%20nursery%2C%20in%20Sanyal%20village%20near%20the%20International%20Border%20with%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20subsequent%20massive%20search%20operation%2C%20involving%20the%20police%2C%20army%2C%20NSG%2C%20BSF%2C%20and%20CRPF%2C%20utilised%20advanced%20technical%20and%20surveillance%20equipment%2C%20including%20helicopters%2C%20UAVs%2C%20drones%2C%20bulletproof%20vehicles%2C%20and%20sniffer%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20teams%20discovered%20evidence%20on%20Monday%2C%20including%20four%20loaded%20magazines%20of%20M4%20carbine%2C%20two%20grenades%2C%20a%20bulletproof%20jacket%2C%20sleeping%20bags%2C%20tracksuits%2C%20food%20packets%2C%20and%20materials%20for%20constructing%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%20(IEDs)%20near%20the%20Hiranagar%20encounter%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20believe%20the%20terrorists%20infiltrated%20on%20Saturday%2C%20possibly%20via%20a%20ravine%20route%20or%20a%20newly%20constructed%20tunnel%20from%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Nalin%20Prabhat%2C%20and%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Jammu%20Zone%2C%20Bhim%20Sen%20Tuti%2C%20have%20been%20overseeing%20the%20anti-terrorist%20operation%20from%20Kathua%20for%20the%20past%20four%20days%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743084420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2F0hm1f7uo_indian-army-generic_625x300_11_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-security-personnel-injured-amid-ongpoing-encounter-in-j-ks-kathua-8025145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fierce%20gun%20battle%20in%20a%20remote%20forested%20area%20of%20Kathua%20district%20has%20left%205%20security%20personnel%20injured%20as%20the%20security%20forces%20intensified%20their%20operation%20to%20neutralise%20an%20infiltrating%20group%20of%20about%205%20terrorists%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-security-personnel-injured-amid-ongpoing-encounter-in-j-ks-kathua-8025145%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20administration%20plans%20large%20layoffs%2C%20targets%2010K%20jobs%20in%20health%20dept%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743083667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-administration-plans-large-layoffs-targets-10k-jobs-in-health-dept-125032701101_1.html%2