ocial%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20unique%20approach%20rooted%20in%20social%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20reduce%20entrepreneurship%20to%20clich%C3%A9s%20instead%20of%20building%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20view.%20Inclusive%20entrepreneurship%20is%20about%20creating%20an%20economy%20where%20millions%20of%20%E2%80%98job%20seekers%E2%80%99%20become%20%E2%80%98job%20makers%E2%80%99%20in%20their%20communities%20while%20prioritising%20social%20inclusion%2C%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20and%20economic%20growth.%20By%20bridging%20skill%20gaps%2C%20co-creating%20with%20communities%2C%20and%20enabling%20entrepreneurial%20ecosystems%2C%20we%20can%20drive%20innovation%2C%20scale%20businesses%2C%20and%20lower%20the%20costs%20of%20setting%20up%20enterprises.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Shrashtant%20Patara%2C%20CEO%2C%20Development%20Alternatives%20Group.%20These%20words%20make%20it%20evident%20what%20sets%20the%20Inclusive%20Entrepreneurship%20programme%20apart%20%E2%80%94%20an%20innovative%2C%20community-driven%20approach.%20The%20idea%20is%20simple%20yet%20profound%3A%20wisdom%20and%20solutions%20lie%20within%20the%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20aspects%20of%20this%20approach%20is%20something%20called%20%E2%80%98deep%20listening%E2%80%99.%20This%20means%20immersing%20fully%20in%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20world%20%E2%80%94%20understanding%20their%20culture%2C%20challenges%2C%20and%20aspirations%20%E2%80%94%20while%20making%20careful%20observations.%20The%20programme%20combines%20deep%20listening%20with%20steps%20like%20%E2%80%9Cco-creation%E2%80%9D%2C%20where%20solutions%20are%20developed%20together%20with%20the%20participants%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprototyping%E2%80%9D%20to%20test%20ideas%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cacceleration%E2%80%9D%20to%20bring%20these%20ideas%20to%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22