e%20the%20idea%20of%20dehydrated%20food%20had%20been%20around%20for%20some%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20soon%20realised%20that%20the%20technique%20they%20wanted%20to%20use%2C%20freeze-drying%2C%20was%20a%20whole%20different%20ballgame.%20Unlike%20the%20conventional%20method%20of%20dehydration%2C%20freeze-drying%20removes%20moisture%20from%20food%20without%20compromising%20its%20structure%2C%20texture%2C%20or%20nutritional%20value.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20technique%20used%20to%20preserve%20food%20for%20astronauts%2C%20ensuring%20they%20have%20nutritious%20meals%20while%20travelling%20in%20space%20for%20extended%20periods%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-1-1-1742740899-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spice%20Up%20Food%20uses%20freeze-drying%20technology%20to%20deliver%20perservative%20free%20ready-to-eat%20meals%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-1-1-1742740899-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-1-1-1742740899-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-1-1-1742740899-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-1-1-1742740899-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-1-1-1742740899-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-03-20-at-20.05.12-1-1-1742740899-600x800.j