er%20Prize%20and%20the%20International%20Stockholm%20Junior%20Water%20Prize%202024.%20At%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20she%20was%20among%20the%2010%20students%20selected%20from%20350%20applicants.%20Her%20ability%20to%20combine%20research%20with%20practical%20implementation%20impressed%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20presented%20the%20pitch%20effectively%2C%20showing%20both%20the%20research%20and%20implementation%20parts%2C%20which%20they%20liked%2C%20and%20I%20highlighted%20my%20project%2C%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20people%20want%20to%20do%20and%20what%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mannat%20shares.%20Winning%20this%20competition%20earned%20her%20the%20opportunity%20to%20represent%20India%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-89-1742799733.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mannat%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20discuss%20her%20mechanism%20with%20industry%20leaders%20like%20Xylem.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-89-1742799733.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-89-1742799733-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-89-1742799733-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-89-1742799733-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-89-1742799733-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-415507%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMannat%20had%20the%20opportu